application_type_full: Prior Approval: Change of use - offices to dwellinghouses
description: Prior approval application in relation to the change of use of the ground to 4th and 6th to 11th floors (inclusive) from B1(a) office to C3 residential creating 150 residential units.
decision_conditions:
CONDITION: On-site bicycle storage, which shall be secure and provide for no less than 159 bicycle spaces, shall be provided prior to the first occupation of the residential units, shall be maintained as such thereafter and no change therefrom shall take place unless otherwise agreed in writing by the Local Planning Authority.

REASON: To ensure adequate bicycle parking is available and easily accessible on site and to promote sustainable modes of transport in accordance with policy 6.9 of the London Plan 2015 (incorporating Minor Alterations 2016), policy CS10 of Islington's Core Strategy 2011, and policy DM8.4 of Islington's Development Management Policies 2013.
